<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SSL 证书安装 - HJSYSTEM</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        
        .warning-box {
            background: rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid #ff9800;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .warning-box h2 {
            color: #ff9800;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .step {
            background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
        }
        
        .step h3 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .step p {
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .download-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #388E3C);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            border: 1.5px solid transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            min-width: 140px;
            outline-offset: 2px;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.5);
        }

        .download-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }

        .download-btn:focus-visible {
            outline: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            outline-offset: 2px;
        }

        .download-btn:disabled,
        .download-btn[disabled] {
            opacity: 0.45;
            cursor: not-allowed !important;
            transform: none !important;
            box-shadow: none !important;
            filter: grayscale(30%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* 下载按钮变体 */
        .download-btn.btn-blue {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2196F3, #1976D2);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: transparent;
        }

        .download-btn.btn-blue:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.5);
        }

        .download-btn.btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .download-btn.btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }
        
        .note {
            background: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #2196F3;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .note h4 {
            color: #2196F3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        code {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            background: rgba(255, 235, 59, 0.3);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #ffeb3b;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        ol.instructions {
            margin-left: 20px;
            line-height: 2;
        }
        
        ol.instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .troubleshooting {
            background: rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #f44336;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .troubleshooting h4 {
            color: #f44336;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .cert-textarea {
            display: none;
        }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>SSL 证书安装向导</h1>
        
        <div class="warning-box">
            <h2>为什么需要安装证书？</h2>
            <p>HJSYSTEM 使用 HTTPS 加密连接保护您的数据安全。由于使用的是自签名证书，浏览器会显示安全警告。安装证书后，警告将消失，您可以正常使用所有功能（包括导出 Excel 选择保存路径）。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
            <h3>步骤 1：下载证书</h3>
            <p>点击下方按钮下载证书文件：</p>
            <button onclick="downloadLocal('ca.crt')" class="download-btn btn-blue">下载证书 (ca.crt)</button>
            <p style="margin-top:10px; color:#aaa; font-size:14px;">下载后双击安装证书</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
            <h3>步骤 2：安装证书</h3>
            <ol class="instructions">
                <li>双击下载的 <code>ca.crt</code> 文件</li>
                <li>在弹出的证书窗口中，点击<span class="highlight">"安装证书"</span>按钮</li>
                <li>选择<span class="highlight">"本地计算机"</span>，点击"下一步"</li>
                <li>选择<span class="highlight">"将所有的证书都放入下列存储"</span>，然后点击"浏览"</li>
                <li>在列表中选择<span class="highlight">"受信任的根证书颁发机构"</span>，点击"确定"</li>
                <li>点击"下一步"，然后点击"完成"</li>
                <li>如果弹出安全警告，点击<span class="highlight">"是"</span>确认安装</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
            <h3>步骤 3：重启浏览器</h3>
            <p><span class="highlight">重要！</span> 必须完全关闭所有浏览器窗口，然后重新打开浏览器，证书才能生效。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
            <h3>步骤 4：访问系统</h3>
            <p>证书安装完成后，访问以下地址：</p>
            <div id="serverUrls" style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <p><code>https://服务器IP:5002/HJ.html</code></p>
            </div>
            <p>安全警告应该已经消失。</p>
            <a href="/HJ.html" class="download-btn btn-blue" style="margin-top: 15px;">立即访问系统</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="troubleshooting">
            <h4>仍然显示不安全？</h4>
            <p>如果安装证书后仍然显示不安全，请按以下顺序排查：</p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px; line-height: 2;">
                <li><strong>1. 确认安装位置正确：</strong>必须安装到<span class="highlight">"受信任的根证书颁发机构"</span>，不是"个人"或"中级证书颁发机构"</li>
                <li><strong>2. 重启浏览器：</strong>完全关闭<strong>所有</strong>浏览器窗口（包括其他标签页），重新打开</li>
                <li><strong>3. 清除缓存：</strong>按 Ctrl+Shift+Delete 清除浏览器缓存和 Cookie</li>
                <li><strong>4. 检查证书有效期：</strong>右键 ca.crt -^> 打开 -^> 查看"有效期"是否在范围内</li>
                <li><strong>5. 检查系统时间：</strong>确保电脑系统时间正确</li>
                <li><strong>6. 重启电脑：</strong>有时需要重启系统才能生效</li>
                <li><strong>7. 重新生成证书：</strong>如果以上都无效，关闭服务器，运行 <code>node regenerate-cert.js</code> 重新生成证书，然后重新安装</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="note" style="background: rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.1); border-color: #ff9800;">
            <h4 style="color: #ff9800;">Edge/Chrome 浏览器特殊说明</h4>
            <p>新版 Edge/Chrome 对自签名证书有更严格的要求。如果安装后仍显示不安全：</p>
            <p>1. 在地址栏输入 <code>chrome://flags/#allow-insecure-localhost</code>（Edge 同理）</p>
            <p>2. 找到 "Allow invalid certificates for resources loaded from localhost"</p>
            <p>3. 将其设置为 <span class="highlight">Enabled</span></p>
            <p>4. 重启浏览器</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="note">
            <h4>提示</h4>
            <p>• 证书只需安装一次，之后访问系统不会再显示安全警告</p>
            <p>• 如果有多台电脑需要访问，每台电脑都需要安装证书</p>
            <p>• 证书有效期为 1 年，过期后需要重新安装</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        // 自动填充当前服务器地址
        var serverOrigin = window.location.origin;
        var serverUrlsDiv = document.getElementById('serverUrls');
        serverUrlsDiv.innerHTML = '<p><code>' + serverOrigin + '/HJ.html</code></p>';

        // 证书内容（嵌入，无需网络请求）
        var CERT_CONTENT = "-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----\nMIIFMzCCAxugAwIBAgIBATANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQsFADA7MRkwFwYDVQQDExBISlNZ\nU1RFTSBSb290IENBMREwDwYDVQQKEwhISlNZU1RFTTELMAkGA1UEBhMCQ04wHhcN\nMjYwNTI5MTAzNDM4WhcNMzYwNTI5MTAzNDM4WjA7MRkwFwYDVQQDExBISlNZU1RF\nTSBSb290IENBMREwDwYDVQQKEwhISlNZU1RFTTELMAkGA1UEBhMCQ04wggIiMA0G\nCSqGSIb3DQEBAQUAA4ICDwAwggIKAoICAQCx/j0mnKu0THsNHocO7PMxkvd83RA/\nZ2ajGMT5TbFhockxoY18kgMPXm4EEGEyolAJ/oRGFbAumDN2wkwG2tLNf+HXutJW\nqiePjM6n/r+my8clfOGcYIs2fe3xglnNyuwN4GAjSHNDbLhPQOPoyonzoOlhIkmX\n7mP79uYyWHStYl0ZPSRA1n/cZVZG7bNlY3PMJFMvQQ9tKDRIQWYsJq3srCsZesn8\n825r5k+EdFWyJzaNE+eRm/qILkmAcQHGph6OvBIXGaXLd3t6UFCqAfaaf0qBqe0k\nRQywqQ8mANwwuDdw7vlMMaV59Qi8WQja+fvxEcUkC4LdWxhy5AtzgZ6vqSlBPeK+\nnVXu5ptw17fA3AO/0od/NNxx3UbGTiXOLlHSlwFZoSlfCxX2Rlz08rLjo94PrHIv\nKSEaat7Ngqs6T+8pAoMSpH80eLbB25SPt//zCYK0HWQvnCdaX2qa4j0oaWWRab2N\nlJ1tqUyb60XYEWieOcT+z1sv17LGa9cnrv+a8IXn0pliOA4GSX2/qw79YN0duX3/\nx75CdpE5G8jx95aG82qobNgAXBWaF0fWQ1AFT6M8+m0vARbncJbSoYa8asb8fcBH\nP+wA6zbrcGBJH1Zr+TKscDy2Y26U3+FXkjLOY06qF80s7CUlSvWyuJTsHfpyJEqi\nZb1CSCsBiNs5kQIDAQABo0IwQDAPBgNVHRMBAf8EBTADAQH/MA4GA1UdDwEB/wQE\nAwIBBjAdBgNVHQ4EFgQU6EjUFMw1dlnaTUdNjkz+1Z+BJJgwDQYJKoZIhvcNAQEL\nBQADggIBACCX8uMnib/eJb+zzXVdNsK9eijZJpYo5HcPoTr8YcExdzTJrfy2tIq2\n1zi4E1/CKp9R+BLde4Ul4Fsaeuebwx/3l+fAXywFuKf368snE7JGKrYuGibs8twV\nSw0AH3Xt9AMw5hmKPKYrJ171r2WlwuKm7EtARo1NSVXYWGm+g22CZSafzWzGlFkq\nWdHSQ5ewT/qnkTWsUjV8oCfdqJrtSSz+rOcdpsWgaxTq7KWjSSvM9VpKGmpdWCQp\nLNJN8nnlp5GUxf4dDVQfvaQJbwcVunLZ6nyQExgffcjwl3I0ruyn/91qgftHl5TT\nHvb5bZm1BLgGpsUdF9Y3vt3sR1YFxlZPTevVfCAKMVuYfbBRzqQ9M7VSvcNPzdKS\nFwxp6HDgUuGlnvLbqXfPW1wRc9/mfcGVOBUl+J3wQc/h1DDWDn59YjXe7LBYGMjP\n3Df3TO+MEYVfMu8AZBYZtp2EhsYM7FglL4CZf8t0avYflD0HTM8z8am7sDtwZ8fC\nkNS2UBMQPAE8MsuCP9N+1Pcq7xq3yzOaySgD+A+ECNjJ7qjBykrcP+f6hA8sjHEO\ny1nzJYXaQtd88YWMrvWs5JuXxracC+MOXTp8ncOHUsf1RJS0oihALNM8zlfy6hnb\nJY8sMb0S8xEPjB6Vv9j//UHAQXgN7KEpcOZPxIuB7ltoxLuIKhGl\n-----END CERTIFICATE-----";

        var BAT_CONTENT = "@echo off\nchcp 65001 >nul\ntitle HJSYSTEM \u8bc1\u4e66\u5b89\u88c5\u5de5\u5177\n\necho ==========================================\necho   HJSYSTEM CA \u8bc1\u4e66\u81ea\u52a8\u5b89\u88c5\u5de5\u5177\necho ==========================================\necho.\n\nset \"SCRIPT_DIR=%~dp0\"\nset \"CERT_FILE=%SCRIPT_DIR%ca.crt\"\n\nif not exist \"%CERT_FILE%\" (\n    echo [\u9519\u8bef] \u672a\u627e\u5230\u8bc1\u4e66\u6587\u4ef6: ca.crt\n    echo \u8bf7\u5c06\u672c\u811a\u672c\u4e0e ca.crt \u653e\u5728\u540c\u4e00\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u8fd0\u884c\u3002\n    pause\n    exit /b 1\n)\n\necho [1/3] \u6b63\u5728\u5220\u9664\u65e7\u7684 HJSYSTEM \u8bc1\u4e66...\ncertutil -delstore Root \"HJSYSTEM\" >nul 2>&1\ncertutil -delstore TrustedPublisher \"HJSYSTEM\" >nul 2>&1\necho [\u5b8c\u6210] \u65e7\u8bc1\u4e66\u5df2\u6e05\u7406\necho.\n\necho [2/3] \u6b63\u5728\u5b89\u88c5 CA \u8bc1\u4e66\u5230\u53d7\u4fe1\u4efb\u6839\u8bc1\u4e66\u9881\u53d1\u673a\u6784...\ncertutil -addstore -f \"Root\" \"%CERT_FILE%\"\nif %errorlevel% neq 0 (\n    echo [\u9519\u8bef] \u8bc1\u4e66\u5b89\u88c5\u5931\u8d25\uff0c\u8bf7\u4ee5\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\u8eab\u4efd\u8fd0\u884c\u672c\u811a\u672c\u3002\n    echo \u53f3\u952e\u70b9\u51fb install-cert.bat \u2192 \u9009\u62e9\"\u4ee5\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\u8eab\u4efd\u8fd0\u884c\"\n    pause\n    exit /b 1\n)\necho [\u5b8c\u6210] CA \u8bc1\u4e66\u5df2\u5b89\u88c5\necho.\n\necho [3/3] \u6b63\u5728\u5b89\u88c5\u5230\u53d7\u4fe1\u4efb\u53d1\u5e03\u8005...\ncertutil -addstore -f \"TrustedPublisher\" \"%CERT_FILE%\" >nul 2>&1\necho [\u5b8c\u6210] \u53d7\u4fe1\u4efb\u53d1\u5e03\u8005\u5df2\u66f4\u65b0\necho.\n\necho ==========================================\necho   \u8bc1\u4e66\u5b89\u88c5\u6210\u529f\uff01\necho ==========================================\necho.\necho \u8bf7\u6309\u4ee5\u4e0b\u6b65\u9aa4\u64cd\u4f5c\uff1a\necho  1. \u5b8c\u5168\u5173\u95ed\u6240\u6709 Edge/Chrome \u6d4f\u89c8\u5668\u7a97\u53e3\necho  2. \u91cd\u65b0\u6253\u5f00\u6d4f\u89c8\u5668\necho  3. \u8bbf\u95ee https://172.16.52.100:5002/HJ.html\necho.\necho \u5982\u679c\u4ecd\u663e\u793a\u4e0d\u5b89\u5168\uff0c\u8bf7\u5c1d\u8bd5\uff1a\necho  \u2022 \u6e05\u9664\u6d4f\u89c8\u5668\u7f13\u5b58 (Ctrl+Shift+Delete)\necho  \u2022 \u91cd\u542f\u7535\u8111\necho.\npause";

        // 证书内容已移除

        // 纯前端下载 — 不依赖网络请求
        function downloadLocal(filename) {
            var content, mime;
            if (filename === 'ca.crt') {
                content = CERT_CONTENT;
                mime = 'application/x-x509-ca-cert';
            } else if (filename === 'install-cert.bat') {
                content = BAT_CONTENT;
                mime = 'application/octet-stream';
            } else {
                alert('\u672a\u77e5\u6587\u4ef6: ' + filename);
                return;
            }
            var blob = new Blob([content], { type: mime + ';charset=utf-8' });
            var url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
            var a = document.createElement('a');
            a.href = url;
            a.download = filename;
            a.style.display = 'none';
            document.body.appendChild(a);
            a.click();
            document.body.removeChild(a);
            setTimeout(function() { URL.revokeObjectURL(url); }, 1000);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
